---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import screenshotLinux from '../assets/images/screenshot-linux.png';
import screenshotWin from '../assets/images/screenshot-win.png';
---
<!-- What it does: screenshot showcase grid -->
<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What it does</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">A system tray icon that monitors your Claude Code API usage in real-time. Hover to see progress bars, model breakdowns, and reset countdowns.</p>

    <div class="showcase-grid">
      <div class="showcase-item">
        <Image src={screenshotLinux} alt="Linux system tray tooltip showing 5-hour and weekly usage progress bars with Claude model breakdown" loading="lazy" format="webp" quality={85} data-lightbox />
        <h3>Linux system tray</h3>
        <p>Pure Go implementation with <code>fyne.io/systray</code>. Displays real-time usage progress bars for 5-hour and weekly windows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-item">
        <Image src={screenshotWin} alt="Windows system tray tooltip showing API usage monitoring with reset timer" loading="lazy" format="webp" quality={85} data-lightbox />
        <h3>Windows & macOS</h3>
        <p>Cross-platform support with native system tray integration. CGO enabled for macOS/Windows builds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-item">
        <div class="showcase-info-card">
          <h3>Live monitoring</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>5-hour usage window progress bar</li>
            <li>Weekly usage progress bar</li>
            <li>Model breakdown (Opus, Sonnet)</li>
            <li>Reset countdown timers</li>
            <li>Throttle detection warnings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h3>Real-time updates</h3>
        <p>Auto-refreshes every 5 minutes from the Anthropic API. OAuth token read from <code>~/.claude/.credentials.json</code>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .showcase-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .showcase-item {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .showcase-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .showcase-item img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.15), 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .showcase-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .showcase-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .showcase-item code {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
  }

  .showcase-info-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .showcase-info-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
  }

  .showcase-info-card ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .showcase-info-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .showcase-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
